
-------
creating a group
-------

groupadd goonerz

-------
adding a user to a group
-------

usermod -G goonerz baker

-------
removing a user from a group
-------

gpasswd -d baker goonerz


-------
removing a group
-------

groupdel goonerz

========
Concept	What it means	Example
Primary group		One default group; used for new files	gid=1001(marcus)
Secondary groups	Extra groups a user belongs to; grants extra permissions, like sudo, docker etc.
